
Lua - Approach
simulation - topmost lua table - set of systems
	systems - systems
	rules - simulation rules - immutable after init, (de)serializable, deterministic to code
	event - simuluation event history - list, append-only, (de)serializable
	state - simulation state - (de)serializable, deterministic to code + inputs
		world
	per system:
		game - game state - optional, encodable
		lv - world state - optional, encodable
		rule - system rules - optional, immutable, encodable


